==Download & Install Processing
http://processing.org/download/

==Installing Processing Textmate Bundle

===Install GetBundles (http://svn.textmate.org/trunk/Review/Bundles/GetBundles.tmbundle/)
  $ cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles
  $ svn co http://svn.textmate.org/trunk/Review/Bundles/GetBundles.tmbundle/

===Install Processing Bundle
  Bundles > Get Bundles > Get Bundles
  Find the Processing Bundle, highlight and click "Install Bundles"

===Fix Bundle Run Command
  Bundles > Bundle Editor > Show Bundles Editor
  Unfold the Processing Bundle
  Highlight "Run in Processing"
  Change instaces of "Processing 0135" (or whatever number it has) to just "Processing"
    (the script should look like this: http://gist.github.com/1ecdd8ac3e09672e1aee)

===Reload Bundles
  Bundles > Bundle Editor > Reload Bundles

===On OS X other Processing Preferences are located here:
  /Users/{your_username}/Library/Processing/preferences.txt